Web site review list

Check list for all websites

Use a system for padding - Base font size set to 16px and use em unite after that. So 1em for padding is 16px. Base 8 gives you a system where you always have even divisions (32, 16, 8, 4, 2, 1, .5, .25, etc) so it makes it easy to do the math and get even spacing.

Review Site on mobile - some elements on mobile are skinny and difficult to look at.

Align all text to the left. Only headers should be aligned to the center. (2 lines max).

Body and sub headings should be left alligned.

Ensure all photo selections are relevant to the website.
Example of it a funiture site use photos of furniture and not fixtures.

Limit the amount of dead links.

